snippet.textDisplay: People point out a lot of the references of the commercial, but one thing most people haven't drawn attention to is how the first shot of the commercial is shot through the transparent glass of the tray. This kind of shot (often using HD go-pros) was fairly common in breaking bad (think of the shot from the point of view of the dryer during Walt's "money laundering") and it was also super innovative at the time.
